{"tid":941923,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MAMA音樂頒獎禮  林俊傑美聲合唱金鍾國！再與內地明星合照！","createTime":"2018-12-15T08:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T10:15:26.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5b9deb48e657e0b63d8d6817d9d6b79d614f7e7c","tid":941923,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:29:20.000Z","msg":"2018MAMA香港場14日晚間7點盛大展開頒獎典禮，JJ林俊傑首次參加典禮，他受邀表演嘉賓，以自彈自唱的療癒美聲開場，唱著《偉大的渺小》，一開口立刻擄獲全場觀眾，尖叫聲四溢。<br />\n<br />\n林俊傑帶來鋼琴自彈自唱，先唱完《偉大的渺小》，接著演唱《不為誰而作的歌》，完美的演唱讓全場觀眾如痴如醉，他把麥克風替給觀眾，台下響起萬人跟著唱的和聲，彷彿變成JJ演唱會。<br />\n<br />\n連續帶來2首歌曲，林俊傑驚喜與好友金鍾國合唱《恨幸福來過》，兩大療癒美聲合作舞台，為典禮掀起另一段演出亮點。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kZKLw2m53cg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkZKLw2m53cg&d=CZC%2BDMS16IBZWuicu0fkRqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6ba7519a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kZKLw2m53cg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pJrBhZc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpJrBhZc.png&h=78e36f7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ff26921aca99d7dc7e3b12ceda44a6bebee7fe7","tid":941923,"uid":204624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:31:00.000Z","msg":"以鍾國一個韓國人嚟講佢啲普通話都算係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8016aaa9755beda07ae9fdd364d27b169ee9dff","tid":941923,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5ff26921aca99d7dc7e3b12ceda44a6bebee7fe7","tid":941923,"uid":204624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:31:00.000Z","msg":"以鍾國一個韓國人嚟講佢啲普通話都算係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"佢好似講英文??"},{"pid":"09dc082f7a172ebd10d6f3c5ad3eb3ab7e9ab798","tid":941923,"uid":14739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:33:28.000Z","msg":"+2哥哥大陸仔黎？？？"},{"pid":"bba4934749b